{"service_name": "IBM Resiliency Consulting Services", "service_id": "7870031287378310", "company_name": "IBM United Kingdom Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     IBM United Kingdom Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     IBM Resiliency Consulting Services\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    As partners, customers and suppliers increasingly demand 24x7 availability, businesses need to ensure they can still operate during unforeseen events. Your staff may not have the expertise or time to implement an enterprise-wide resilience program. IBM Resiliency Consulting Services provides assistance developing, implementing, testing and managing your business resilience program.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Crisis Management Team structure\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     BCM Review / Audit (BS25999, BS25777)\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Risk Assessment\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Business Impact Analysis\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Recoverability Assessment\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Strategy Development and Implementation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Recovery (BC/DR) Plan development/mentoring\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     BCP Development, Exercising and Maintenance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     BCX.\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     40+ years of business continuity and disaster recovery experience\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     IBM offers a business-focused, robust view of infrastructure risk\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Extensive intellectual property\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provide methodologies for systematic monitoring and IT risk management\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3880 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92284/7870031287378310-pricing-document-2015-09-28-1422.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92284/7870031287378310-sfia-rate-card-2015-10-05-1450.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92284/7870031287378310-service-definition-document-2015-09-28-1336.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92284/7870031287378310-terms-and-conditions-2015-09-28-1421.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <sp